üîÑ INVERTING SCORES (counting red parameters):
   Arousal healthy: 0 ‚Üí Stress points: 1
   Relaxation healthy: 0 ‚Üí Stress points: 1
   Regeneration healthy: 1 ‚Üí Stress points: 0

üìä STRESS TOTAL: 1 + 1 + 0 = 2/3
üí° Interpretation: 2/3 = 2 red parameters (unhealthy)
```

