## Color Legend

### Stress & Burnout:
- üü¢ **Low (0/3)**: No stress, excellent mental health
- üî¥ **Medium (1-2/3)**: Some stress, needs attention
- üî¥ **High (3/3)**: High stress, immediate intervention needed

### Other Parameters:
- üü¢ **High (3/3)**: Excellent function
- üîµ **Medium (2/3)**: Moderate function
- üü† **Low (0-1/3)**: Poor function

